import {
  Button,
  Container,
  Content,
  Form,
  Input,
  Page,
  Title,
  Wrapper,
} from "./styled";

export default function Login() {
  return (
    <Page>
      <Content>
        <Wrapper>
          <Title>Вход</Title>
          <Form>
            <Input placeholder="Логин" $width="" />
            <Input placeholder="Пароль" />
            <Container>
              <Button type="submit" $width="126px" $white>
                Войти
              </Button>
              <Button $width="210px">Регистрация</Button>
            </Container>
          </Form>
        </Wrapper>
      </Content>
    </Page>
  );
}
